Publications More details on the applications and a characterization of their behavior can be found at "An Open-Source Benchmark Suite for Microservices and Their Hardware-Software Implications for Cloud and Edge Systems", Y. Gan et al., ASPLOS 2019.  If you use this benchmark suite in your work, we ask that you please cite the paper above.
